& $\Vsub$ Laplacian eigenvalues / shell decomposition; mass-coefficient assignment map
& \textsf{[Mod]}
& \cite{SmartV, SmartVRev}; nine forward chain coefficients verified at exact rational precision (App.~\ref{app:field-signature-audit}~B)\\
