& $H_4$ / 600-cell active selection; preregistered EEG / chess / HCP witness
& \textsf{[Mod]}
& \cite{SmartARIAChess}; 18/18 + 6/6 + HCP degree-homogeneity at $-11.58\sigma$ (clustering separately $+6.80\sigma$); App.~\ref{app:field-signature-audit}~F\\
